}{\plain \fs24 \b D. Economics\par
}{\plain \fs24 \b 1. AT {\u8220\'93}Eminent domain promotes economic development.{\u8221\'94}\par
}{\plain \fs24 \tab (1) Eminent domain isn{\u8217\'92}t needed for land assembly since secret buyers can solve for \softline
holdouts. If people don{\u8217\'92}t know that a large firm needs their land they have no reason to expect \softline
that holding out would lead to a better price. Without holdouts, takings are never needed since \softline
